8.2 Next Document in Series

This framework (Layer 1: Prevention) is the first of five documents in
the Defect Management System:

1.  **Prevention & Design Review Framework** --- this document

2.  **Verification & Test Execution Framework** --- test case
    architecture, execution pipeline, oracle management

3.  **Defect Monitoring Dashboard Specification** --- unified dashboard
    design, data sources, alerting

4.  **Defect Resolution & Prioritized Backlog Process** --- SLAs,
    escalation paths, fix verification workflow

5.  **Unified Defect Taxonomy & Metrics** --- cross-cutting taxonomy
    (Section 2 of this doc, expanded), KPIs, reporting
